<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
    <p class="lead">Thank you for visiting my website.</p>
    <p>
        Our service provides data on IP addresses.
    </p>

    <p>
        To get data you need to type in the address bar
        @String.Format("{0}://{1}/api/Ips/ ip in format Number-Number-Number-Number", Request.Url.Scheme, Request.Url.Authority).
